A cyberpunk cityscape at night with towering neon-lit servers acting as massive buildings, streams of glowing data flowing between them like rivers. In the foreground, a translucent digital membrane stretches across the scene, filtering the data streams - some particles pass through while others are caught and dissolved. The membrane pulses with electric blue and magenta energy. Rain falls through holographic advertisements, and the wet streets below reflect the chaotic light show above. The atmosphere is dense with fog and digital artifacts, creating depth between the raw data source on one side and the purified, organized streams emerging on the other.
